desc: Shop Shepherd's Online for home delivery of a premium range of sourdough, pastries, sweets and Nice Kitty clean treats across Sydney, Canberra and NSW.

layout.text: Shop your favourite artisan sourdough bread, pies, pastries, gluten free goodies and more from the comfort of your sofa!
Choose from Home Delivery via Sendle shipping OR Click & Collect, which is available at no charge via our four Sydney locations.
